thread.title: Wallace Lovett
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Wallace Lovett

author: Wallace Lovett
title: Wallace Lovett
text: I did have an episode a year or 2 back, in regards to the change of ink packaging. Now I know the packaging doesn't affect the ink, however it wasn't just the packaging that had change more precisely the cartridge differed in other ways which I believed affected the performance of my printer, suffice to say I no longer use that printer, I had to buy another one I've recently purchased ink for this printer from inkstation and lo and behold the packaging & the cartridge have gone back to what they were when I first purchased ink from inkstation.
